      "lang": "javascript",
      "content": "const arr = ['a', 'b', 'c'];\n\nfor (let i = 0; i < arr.length; i = i + 1) {\n  console.log(i, arr[i]);\n}\n// 0 'a'\n// 1 'b'\n// 2 'c'",
